OL,3,CJohn Swinney to host first meeting of
OL,4,C'streamlined' Scottish cabinet
OL,6,FJohn Swinney has vowed that his new-
OL,7,Flook cabinet team will "waste no time
OL,8,Fin delivering" as they prepare to meet
OL,9,Ffor the first time.
OL,11,FThe Scottish First Minister announced
OL,12,Fa scaled-down cabinet earlier this
OL,13,Fweek, which he declared would be
OL,14,Ftasked with "delivering on the
OL,15,Fpriorities of the people of Scotland".
OL,17,FFormer education secretary Jenny
OL,18,FGilruth was promoted to deputy First
OL,19,FMinister in the shake-up, and also
OL,20,Fgiven responsibility for the finance
OL,21,Fbrief.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@NO]vD@MOUwD@eO]
