PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779429952
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to host first meeting of
OL,4,C'streamlined' Scottish cabinet
OL,6,FThat remit will see her working
OL,7,Fclosely with Ivan McKee, who has been
OL,8,Fhanded the new role of Public Service
OL,9,FReform Secretary ` a key appointment
OL,10,Fas the Scottish Government looks to
OL,11,Fdeal with a funding shortfall that
OL,12,Fcould rise to #4.7 billion by the end
OL,13,Fof this decade.
OL,15,FMr Swinney said he was "delighted" to
OL,16,Fbe chairing the first meeting of the
OL,17,Fnew-look cabinet on Friday.
OL,26,@wD@XOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
