OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779429952
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to host first meeting of
OL,4,C'streamlined' Scottish cabinet
OL,6,FThe First Minister said: "The
OL,7,Fministerial team I have appointed will
OL,8,Fbe focused on and responsive to the
OL,9,Fchallenges facing communities across
OL,10,Fthe country.
OL,12,F"That means supporting families
OL,13,Fthrough the current cost-of-living
OL,14,Fcrisis, continuing to deliver
OL,15,Fimprovements in our NHS, and growing
OL,16,Four economy ` all of which will
OL,17,Frequire a concerted effort by the
OL,18,Fentire government working together."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUtD@AOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779429952
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to host first meeting of
OL,4,C'streamlined' Scottish cabinet
OL,6,FHe continued: "My new, leaner cabinet
OL,7,Fwill drive that work with greater
OL,8,Fpurpose, co-ordination and
OL,9,Feffectiveness.
OL,11,F"It will help me ensure the government
OL,12,Fhas a clear focus on the changes
OL,13,Fneeded to deliver success, underpinned
OL,14,Fby our commitment to always be on
OL,15,FScotland's side.
OL,17,F"The ministers gathered round the
OL,18,Fcabinet table all possess the
OL,19,Fexperience, skills, talent and the
OL,20,Fdrive needed to deliver lasting change
OL,21,Ffor Scotland.
OL,26,@nD@OOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779429952
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to host first meeting of
OL,4,C'streamlined' Scottish cabinet
OL,6,F"We have a vision to take our country
OL,7,Fforward, and we will waste no time in
OL,8,Fdelivering progress."
OL,10,FHowever, his appointments drew
OL,11,Fcriticism from opposition parties at
OL,12,FHolyrood, with Meghan Gallacher of the
OL,13,FConservatives saying it appeared Mr
OL,14,FSwinney's government "had been on
OL,15,FMounjaro because it has slimmed down
OL,16,Fin size" but adding despite this it
OL,17,F"still somehow carries all the same
OL,18,Fpolitical baggage".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]vD@VOUxD@HO]yD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
