PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779429952
OL,3,CJohn Swinney to host first meeting of
OL,4,C'streamlined' Scottish cabinet
OL,6,FShe said: "We now have a government
OL,7,Fwhere the cabinet looks exhausted
OL,8,Falready, and they haven't even
OL,9,Fdelivered their first Programme for
OL,10,FGovernment."
OL,12,FReform UK's Scottish deputy leader
OL,13,FThomas Kerr said the new cabinet team
OL,14,Fwas "tired and knackered".
OL,16,FHe insisted: "Scotland does not need
OL,17,Fanother recycled government pretending
OL,18,Fto be revolutionaries. What Scotland
OL,19,Fneeds is seriousness, competence and
OL,20,Faccountability."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@LO]vD@EOUvD@YO]xD@NOU|D@PO]
